{"tid":401414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現屆議員有人叫何傻賢？","createTime":"2017-09-15T14:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T16:25:05.000Z","uid":22736,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a12a44483afbefeeabb7159edb62516f484831","tid":401414,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"仲有約兩個星期就到10月1，好多愛國愛港團體開始陸續寄出中國國慶活動請柬，呢類慶祝活動又點少得請官員同建制派議員做嘉賓！今日網上就傳出一張相，原來係香港南區各界慶祝國慶68周年聯歡晚會嘅請柬，但最有趣係入面嘉賓名單，竟然有一位係立法會議員「何傻賢」！<br />\n八方諗究竟邊個係「何傻賢」？諗咗一輪應該係主辦單位印錯立法會漁農界議員何俊賢個名做「何傻賢」，八方打電話問何俊賢點睇，但佢就冇覆電話，不過佢回應其他傳媒就話唔介意，又話主辦單位已打過電話畀佢道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/224925_7f84373faf35618c8dc308646791e0ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F224925_7f84373faf35618c8dc308646791e0ff.jpg&h=2675cba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98b87a184ed3757b8284e8a36bb2791686d890e1","tid":401414,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"haha"},{"pid":"3b95aa4b5ffdd19c9a646386f50390e84fa873e9","tid":401414,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"襯晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadec70fee8a2840cb184878da936ec4799505b6","tid":401414,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"其實呢個先係佢嘅真名"},{"pid":"9a2339cf61d344533d30d8f35e149eb77db39e02","tid":401414,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1924da68fd6f50ffe8b93903c3e95974034c7c48","tid":401414,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"傻賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2455d25018773457a562a54ae250e58850de5cd6","tid":401414,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:13:53.000Z","msg":"新亞書院校董會副主席陳志新認為，「傻賢」二字相當敏感，學生嘅解釋喺邏輯上唔能夠接受，「(外界)不是沒有智慧，(寫錯)何『好』賢都可以，但寫錯做何『傻』賢&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"c4c862c964e2b867aeb0c318f7097cb08f459179","tid":401414,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新亞書院校董會副主席陳志新認為，「傻賢」二字相當敏感，學生嘅解釋喺邏輯上唔能夠接受，「(外界)不是沒有智慧，(寫錯)何『好』賢都可以，但寫錯做何『傻』賢&hellip;&hellip;」</blockquote><br />\n寫佢老母咩 擺明就電腦搞<br />\n如果用速成打條撚樣個字 傻同俊都係一樣打法出錯有乜咁奇 打左好字就真係玩野啦"}]}